WHO warning message function
Double mode,each of the 90 set of measurements of memory

The clock feature

Condition: new 
Product size: 71*73*32mm (wristband not included) 
Wristband range: 135~195mm 
Display: LCD digital display screen 
Measurement range: blood pressure 0~280mmHg pulse 40~199 times / min

name: Geriatric Recliner Chair with wheels
description:
The Mobile Reclining Geriatric Chair with Tray provides a sturdy and comfortable seat at home for users who sit for longer periods of time. It includes wheels so you can reposition the chair in other areas of the house, and can be reclined to different positions for greater comfort.

-Manual reclining backrest: 115° (upright), 135°, 145°, 155° (maximum recline)
-Automatic elevating footrest
-Swivel castor wheels for easy transportation of patient within the house
-High contoured, thick padded seat back to provide lumbar support
-Flip-up lap tray can be stowed away
-Adjustable headrest
-Includes seat belt
-Available in fixed-height armrest and adjustable-height option
